      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18691&rangeEnd=18776",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18691&rangeEnd=18776"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_7_1858-1946",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1858-1946",
      "markText": "我决定接受这位父亲的捐赠，说实话，我只是担心所有这些财富会落到坏人的手中，担心他找到的那个分享财富的人在社会上用它们来犯罪，而不是像我打算做的那样，用来为众人造福，为上天增光。",
      "totalCount": 1224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1858&rangeEnd=1946",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1858&rangeEnd=1946"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_6_6920-6947",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6920-6947",
      "markText": "您要是指责我向您表白爱意，那您也要责怪您自己艳色绝世。",
