      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2498&rangeEnd=2542",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2498&rangeEnd=2542"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_6_12937-13033",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "12937-13033",
      "markText": "是的，孽种，今晚就办婚事，把你们都气死。啊！我就要跟你们所有的人对着干，让你们知道我是一家之主，在这里，所有的事情都由我说了算。小无赖，就这样，你把先前说过的话收回去，马上跪在他脚下求他宽恕。",
      "totalCount": 1008,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12937&rangeEnd=13033",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12937&rangeEnd=13033"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_5_5464-5499",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5464-5499",
      "markText": "您这是要他踩着您的钟点去教堂，就像那些只为了让您看见才去那里的人一样？",
      "totalCount": 990,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5464&rangeEnd=5499",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5464&rangeEnd=5499"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_4_11226-11286",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "11226-11286",
      "markText": "他教我对任何事都不要热心，他让我甩掉心中的一切友情；我可以看着我的兄弟、孩子、母亲和妻子一个个死去，死了我也全然不在乎。",
      "totalCount": 984,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11226&rangeEnd=11286",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11226&rangeEnd=11286"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_6_2601-2699",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2601-2699",
      "markText": "这说明您是多么经不起诱惑，肉体对您的感官能产生这么大的影响？我当然不知道您心里往上蹿的是什么火，可是我，我可没那么容易看到什么东西就垂涎欲滴，就算您从头到脚赤身裸体，那一身皮囊也休想让我心荡神迷。",
      "totalCount": 976,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2601&rangeEnd=2699",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2601&rangeEnd=2699"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_4_11833-11866",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "11833-11866",
      "markText": "有一天，他甚至捶胸顿足，因为当时他在祷告，很气愤地弄死了一只跳蚤。",
      "totalCount": 867,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11833&rangeEnd=11866",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11833&rangeEnd=11866"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_4_11724-11770",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "11724-11770",
      "markText": "为了我的名誉，对我的妻子也嘘寒问暖；他提醒我哪些人对她脉脉含情，发出比我还要大五六倍的醋劲。",
      "totalCount": 852,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11724&rangeEnd=11770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11724&rangeEnd=11770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_5_2384-2414",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2384-2414",
      "markText": "可我想让它变成事实；我已经替你做出决定，你只需对我言听计从。",
      "totalCount": 804,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2384&rangeEnd=2414",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2384&rangeEnd=2414"
