    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300054932_7_10426-10475",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10426-10475",
      "markText": "假如只是上帝阻碍我实现愿望，那么去掉这样的一个障碍对我来说并不算什么事，这不该成为您心中的绊脚石。",
      "totalCount": 768,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300054932&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10426&rangeEnd=10475",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1c732b80813ab7bf5g012052?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10426&rangeEnd=10475"
    },
    {
